itemLabel: Paul Wilson, Baron Wilson of High Wray

wikipedia_page.main: Paul Norman Wilson, Baron Wilson of High Wray   (24 October 1908 – 24 February 1980) was a British engineer, Lord Lieutenant of Westmorland (1965 to 1974) and of Cumbria (1974 to 1980) and Governor of the BBC.
